{"tid":1594272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港所有連儂牆admin請入一入黎 ~ 中共黑歷史文宣","createTime":"2019-09-25T13:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T19:16:14.000Z","uid":294,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9621977dabd88c9493ce2abe3095097937b2d3","tid":1594272,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一個tg谷&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">歷史黨案館</span>&rdquo;既成員，之前係連登成立既，目的係想係929之前在各區連儂牆貼上<span style=\"color: red;\">中共70年大事回顧</span>，等大家認識中共既真面目，又可大事慶祝國殤日。<br />\n我地現正在埋尾階段，預計完成後大概我有<span style=\"color: red;\">60張A4及40張A3 文宣海報</span>想張貼係主要連儂牆。（由於呢個project會有大概共100張文宣，如果你管理的連儂牆唔夠位，可以重點貼上我地既A3主打文宣。）<br />\n<br />\n請問各位你的連儂牆可以貼上我地既文宣嗎？如果可以的話，我地會提供文宣檔案同排版方法，請各區admin自行安排印刷，各區自付印刷費（其實每區應該唔會超過$200)。各區須要預留空位和在929前幫忙貼上，我地亦會有成員落黎幫忙，如有興趣參加，誠邀你加入我地谷，以獲取最新update：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OvoXFFRQlVHwvQnrq4ON7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOvoXFFRQlVHwvQnrq4ON7A&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a0d6dec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OvoXFFRQlVHwvQnrq4ON7A</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(代po, by 會員孫中山個仔)</span>"},{"pid":"c57ba59bcea7a9bedefeb1b37555707ceb928c6a","tid":1594272,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"#929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism<br />\n#929GlobalMarch"},{"pid":"09de85e2e53f5836f5a3dfa73e3b47f63048eaf7","tid":1594272,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"#929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism<br />\n#929GlobalMarch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0889cabdbb2942053b277bd2ee8c2949e27983e","tid":1594272,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"#929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism<br />\n#929GlobalMarch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" cl